The surges of ley-line energy have been increasing. They're concentrating into new and more dangerous forms. These anomalies don't appear to be hostile, but their presence is causing a lot of damage. We can't let them continue this destruction. I have something for you that could help. Come see me as soon as you can.

—Ela Makkay
